<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">The Republic of China 's</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">tenth</ENAMEX> - term president and vice president , <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Chen Shui - bian</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Annette Lu</ENAMEX> , took the oath of office on <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">20 May , 2000</ENAMEX> in the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">first</ENAMEX> - ever transfer of power in <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Chinese</ENAMEX> history to a popularly elected leader from the opposition .
